	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>Tuesday&#44; 16 Adar&#44; 1865</date>.</p>
				<p>My friend and dear one&#44; dear to my soul&#44; dear friend&#59;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">You are forgetting me entirely. Herewith you receive 2<lb/> articles which you will translate letter for letter.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Unfortunately&#44; I have been ill for weeks. I get lower<lb/> in body <sic>inspirit</sic>. I can no longer work as I used to. I lack the sphere<lb/> of influence that I want.</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">Your friend&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">Jonah</persName></p>
				<p>Through whom will I receive the copies for <date>March</date>. Shall I send you a<lb/> report about the <date>Purim</date> Ball of today&#63;</p>
